e_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "70 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/619283324"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I9pHI4JeIta5uEAMaCDk5ODk4NjMxIInapqcGMAA4JUAUcgk2MTkyODMzMjR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "21_1693044162.788701", "card_id": "Q_619131015", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 323}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "美国坚称「支持日本排海」，却是 2023 年上半年减少进口日本有关产品最多的国家，如何评价其行为？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "（观察者网讯）8 月 24 日，日本单方面强行启动核污染水排海，将风险转嫁给全世界，引发多国质疑与声讨，而诸多一贯打着环保旗号的西方欧美国家却集体保持沉默。与此同时，美国国务院当天称对日本核污水排海感到「满意」，美驻日大使亦大赞日本排海恶行，还声称要在本月底访问福岛品尝海鲜，为日本「撑腰」之意不言而喻。 \t 然而事实上，虽然美国在 2 年前就宣称撤销了对日本食品进口的限制，摆出一副对日本食品来者不拒的欢迎姿态，但根据日本农林水产省 8 月发布的最新数据，美国是今年上半年减少进口日本农林水产品最多的国家，并且主要减少的三种食品——日本酒、鱼糜、扇贝，后两者的主产地均涉及核污染水排放影响区域。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-7f6e2fe090198aed9c1e271ef27597a3_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "67 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/619131015"}}, "attached_info": "ClUI9pHI4JeIta5uEAMaCDk5ODY0NzYzINHkoacGMAA4rAVAFXIJNjE5MTMxMDE1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "22_1693044162.789601", "card_id": "Q_614078642", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 78}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "「可以不谈恋爱，但是一定得有搭子」？「搭子」为什么对新职人这么重要？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-63b72c4d9a2fa24f15785181437cca75_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "64 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/qu