 46%。而较晚开始吸烟者成功戒烟的比例为 56%。研究称建议将买烟的法定年龄提至 22 岁，20 岁前上瘾程度高 _ 科学湃 _ 澎湃新闻 -The Paper"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "4.3 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/619262940"}}, "attached_info": "ClQI9pHI4JeIta5uEAMaCDk5ODk0MTM1II3epacGMAA4IUAicgk2MTkyNjI5NDB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "35_1693044162.806436", "card_id": "Q_618909421", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 63}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有什么东西会让你觉得「提高了生活质量」？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-5c33fc89ec97e1cdbba3505f61ff1200_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "4.3 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/618909421"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I9pHI4JeIta5uEAMaCDk5ODE1NDkxIL2qm6cGMAA4sAFAI3IJNjE4OTA5NDIxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "36_1693044162.806967", "card_id": "Q_601040553", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 53}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价黄晓明、闫妮主演的电影《最后的真相》？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-cf51e900960e6a8faac25ad32b4931f0_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "4.3 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/601040553"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I9pHI4JeIta5uEAMaCDk1ODQ1MDE0ILa6hqMGMAA4UEAkcgk2MDEwNDA1NTN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "37_1693044162.808127", "card_id": "Q_619068908", "feed_specific": {